0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d20727392964909b46d924217aea15919497f5","tid":1933763,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"107f862a56e1173673e584b153079e3c70995e96","tid":1933763,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"笑鳩人前線黃嗰啲撚樣出嚟啦"},{"pid":"34376c2974d4a7dff3481d92337a99c6f7043800","tid":1933763,"uid":205552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"Wtf"},{"pid":"e57a2ccd7fb58944f178bf2767d3a69f1a8f030a","tid":1933763,"uid":311412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c38c9d62900613dd1583a26f3e65a9d7eab8955f","tid":1933763,"uid":306598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"330b63f75ae24e13cbb468c7e9cc955956b69d48","tid":1933763,"uid":335434,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d749256d8251c83c67c2292c23a772f952aab9b1","tid":1933763,"uid":306598,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"律政司已經淪為政治工具，同警隊冇分別，係黃絲點解仲繼續做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"其實打官司上到庭打得柒好難有人咬得你入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"其實我好懷疑咁做嘅作用有幾大，依嫁連告咩罪都係由高層決定，你打得幾柒都好，有充分證據上呈都可以咬得入。如果潛伏喺入面，對抗爭有大幫助，我唔反對，但我嘅質疑係潛伏嘅效用有幾大?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實打官司上到庭打得柒好難有人咬得你入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解<br />\n<br />\n我遇過做檢控既人主要有兩種:<br />\n(1) 仲記得讀 law 既時候教刑事司法制度係要確保疑犯有公平既審訊<br />\n(2) 成L日諗住要釘晒所有疑犯 (同黑警既心態差唔多)<br />\n<br />\n(1) 既人做既事其實係跟住檢控守則3.2段：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>3.2   加拿大最高法院法官Rand在Boucher 訴 女皇 [1955] SCR 16 一案第23及24頁指出：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;必須強調一點，就是刑事檢控的目的，並非為求取定罪，而是要將控方認為與所指稱罪行相關的可信證據，向陪審團展示。檢察官有責任確保展示有關事實的全部所得法律證據：展示證據須鍥而不捨，在合法情況下據理力爭，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但也須公正持平。檢控人員不可存有任何勝敗之心；其職能純粹是為公眾服務</span></strong>，在所有公職人員當中，他承擔的個人責任，無人能及。檢控人員應本著司法程序固有的威信、尊嚴和公義感，有效地履行其職責。＂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你諗到你唔做就會大把(2)既人去做，你就會想繼續做......<br />\n<br />\n同埋做檢控既除左律政司入面既人之外，仲有外面私人執業由律政司外聘既"},{"pid":"f086d8ab4df6bc3511a291da264cda3e8527b6f2","tid":1933763,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/wearebluec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwearebluec&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=842cfdfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wearebluec</a><br />\n藍絲文宣group，入去report佢呀！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snxnQWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnxnQWC.jpg&h=f0b6ba5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"743a91c9ac57d2f8c044b90e0dc70ded2b3f40d2","tid":1933763,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"920a2472291a2d49103ee17ed1715deba260d2a4","tid":1933763,"uid":335434,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"be76c81a3c569e7439f3c7f448ce2cd26f4296db","tid":1933763,"uid":77092,"like":147,"dislike":0,"score":147,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"其實喺律政司黃絲唔係少數  <br />\n近呢半年大把case下面評估過話唔夠料告但極高層堅持要告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:47:33.000Z","msg":"又嚟前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b4c317e49a1fb714c3bce1f96a6ea04cef94da","tid":1933763,"uid":48067,"